It looks like all of the docs have been deleted?

title: What happened to the documentation on Grant Types under OAuth2?

text: Documentation would really be nice given the recent OIDC changes that have seemed to change the default behavior.

Not sure why, but I did stumble across a different branch on RTD 'stable' where documentation has been retained. It's no longer in git master though.

https://oauthlib.readthedocs.io/en/stable/oauth2/grants/authcode.html
